# ThiefGuard â€“ Automatic Thief Detector

## Description
**ThiefGuard** is an AI-powered home security system designed to detect unauthorized entry and alert homeowners instantly. Using motion sensors and a camera, it captures images of intruders and sends notifications to the user, helping prevent theft and secure homes.  

## Technologies Used
- Arduino UNO  
- Raspberry Pi  
- Python (OpenCV)  
- PIR Motion Sensor  

## Key Features
- Real-time motion detection  
- Image capture of intruders  
- Instant notifications via mobile device  
- Easy-to-install and cost-effective  

## My Role
Designed the hardware setup, implemented the Python code for detection and alerts, and tested the full system for reliability.  



